# Chandni Poddar вЂ” Portfolio CMS Implementation Plan

A premium, fully dynamic Portfolio Management System built with **Next.js 15**, **TypeScript**, **Tailwind CSS**, **MongoDB Atlas**, **Cloudinary**, and **NextAuth**.

---

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Before execution begins, please confirm the following:**
> 1. **MongoDB Atlas URI** вЂ“ Do you have an Atlas cluster ready? (We'll use a placeholder env var)
> 2. **Cloudinary Account** вЂ“ Do you have a Cloudinary account? (We'll need `CLOUD_NAME`, `API_KEY`, `API_SECRET`)
