> 4. **Domain / Vercel Project** вЂ“ Do you want a custom domain or use `.vercel.app`?
> 5. **Phase** вЂ“ Should I build **Phase 1 (MVP)** first or the full system? *(Recommended: Phase 1 first)*

> [!WARNING]
> This plan scopes **Phase 1 MVP** for the initial build. Phase 2 (Blog, Analytics, AI, Multi-admin) will follow after user approval of Phase 1.

