### Sprint 4 вЂ” Admin Dashboard (Phase 1 CMS)

#### Admin Login
- Glass card on gradient background with floating shapes
- `next-auth` credentials provider, JWT session
- Bcrypt password verification
- Protected by `middleware.ts` (redirects `/admin/*` if not authenticated)

#### Dashboard Home
- Stats widgets: Total Projects, Skills, Certificates, Messages
- Count-up animation on widget numbers
- Recent contact messages table
- Quick action links

#### Admin Sidebar
- Collapsible animated sidebar
- Icons via `lucide-react`
- Active route highlight

#### CMS Modules (Phase 1)
| Module | Features |
|--------|---------|
| **Hero Manager** | Edit name/designation/tagline, upload profile image, upload resume, update social links |
| **Skills** | Add/Edit/Delete skill, assign category, set icon, reorder |
| **Experience** | Add/Edit/Delete, upload company logo, drag-to-reorder |
| **Projects** | Rich editor, upload image, tech stack tags, featured toggle, category, GitHub/Live URLs |
| **Achievements** | Add/Edit/Delete, upload image, date picker |
| **Certificates** | Add/Edit/Delete, upload certificate image, credential URL |
| **Education** | Add/Edit/Delete education entries |
| **Resume** | Upload/replace PDF, version history display |
| **Messages** | Inbox view (Gmail-style), mark read/unread, delete |

