### Sprint 5 вЂ” SEO, Performance, Polish

- `generateMetadata()` in every page
- Open Graph tags for social sharing
- `sitemap.ts` auto-generation
- `robots.txt`
- `next/image` for all images (automatic optimization)
- `dynamic()` imports for heavy components
- ISR (`revalidate = 3600`) on data-fetching pages
- Error boundaries (`error.tsx`, `not-found.tsx`)
- Loading skeletons (`loading.tsx`)
- Toast notifications via `sonner`
- Full mobile responsiveness (mobile-first Tailwind)
- Dark mode (default) with light mode toggle

